The mirmach trees in this part of the orchard are closely bunched together, making it hard to see further into the rest of the orchard. It seems as if the trees have been specifically planted to achieve the effect of blocking the rest of the orchard. Nevertheless, two narrow paths continue into the rest of the orchard.
