NUMBER 1034
NAME Under Keep, basement
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Flickering shadows dance across an impressive marble arch to the south. Light flows through an opening to the north that leads back into Malthesia's Laboratory. Cobwebs obscure most of the arch, while dust lies thick and heavy upon the floor of the stone chamber. Faint noises emanate from within the dark interior of the mysterious arch...
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=187 VAL2=3945
ITEM 1 72 VAL2=3944
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The lurid visages of demon faces, their mouths set in snarls, stare out at you from their positions upon the arch. The cobwebs sway to and fro in the slight breeze that emanates from within the arch. Pushing aside some of the wispy strands you notice that there is something written upon the face of the arch.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
    "Pass ye beyond this arch and look upon the face of your death!"
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER The sounds emanating from within the arch are muffled, but you can definitely pick out what seems to be the angry howling of some beast and the screeching of claws against stone.
  ECHO OTHERS %N cocks %h head to one side and stares intently at the arch, straining to hear...
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
  ECHO PLAYER You nearly gag as the overpowering stench of death and decay hits your nostrils. The odor barely hides the smell of something strange...alien...mysterious....
  ECHO OTHERS %N gags after taking a deep breath.
ENDIF
IFVERB GO 0
 ECHO PLAYER A cold chill washes over you as you enter the darkness...
 ECHO OTHERS %N gulps and passes through the arch.
ENDIF
