A fiery reddish-orange light emanates from the walls to illuminate this section of the passage. The polished black floor eerily reflects the glow, giving it the appearance of having tiny fire elementals dancing along its surface. The light flickers up towards the ceiling like a fire that is burning out of control, exposing the rows upon rows of leering skulls that cover the entire roof. A palpable inky darkness lies to the east while the passage opens up into a larger room to the west.
