IFSAY heed_my_call,_baron_samark,_I_summon_thee_forth!
 IFVAR INTNUM43 = 90
  ECHO PLAYER You intone the words and instantly feel a cold rush over your body as all the lights in the room dim...
  ECHO OTHERS %N intones the words and you instantly feel a cold rush over your body as ll the lighs in the room dim...
  ECHO ALL %c%cA misty darkness hovers over the altar, slowly shaping and forming itself into a giant Darakoth....It sneers at you contemptously, but there is a glimmer of fear in your eyes....you feel it straining against the magical bonds %N has placed around it with %h words...It speaks, "I am Baron Samark! This was foolish of you mortals...." then begins gesturing....
  EQUAL INTNUM43 110
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY by_the_name,_Ghir,_I_destroy_thee!
 IFVAR INTNUM43 = 110
   ECHO ALL Baron Samark screams in agony as %N yells the words with strong force and conviction! Snarling insanely Baron Samark leaps at %N...%c%c%c
   ECHO ALL A black mist covers the two combatants, you hear horrible screams of agony and pain as the battle shakes the room around you...after what seems to be an eternity...%N staggers forth from the cloud and collapses, pale-faced and shaking before you....%S whispers, "Baron Samark is no more...", then smiles faintly...
   AWARD 58 95000
   EQUAL INTNUM43 130
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH 3
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR demhead2 ! 1
   EQUAL demhead 0
    IFVAR demhead1 = 0
     ECHO PLAYER You hear a slight click as the head slides partway into the wall.
     ECHO OTHERS You hear a faint click as %N pushes the %a partway into the wall.
     EQUAL demhead1 1
     EQUAL demhead 1
    ENDIF
     IFVAR demhead1 ! 0
      IFVAR demhead ! 1
       ECHO PLAYER Loud laughter issues from the head, at the same time as it spews a cone of frost at you!
       ECHO OTHERS %N's efforts to push the %a are met by derisive laughter and a cone of frost!
       DAMAGE COLD 200 Intense cold covers %N!
       EQUAL demhead1 0
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH 2
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR demhead2 ! 1
   EQUAL demhead 0
    IFVAR demhead1 = 1
     ECHO PLAYER You hear a slight click as the head slides partway into the wall.
     ECHO OTHERS You hear a faint click as %N pushes the %a partway into the wall.
     EQUAL demhead1 2
     EQUAL demhead 1
    ENDIF
     IFVAR demhead1 ! 1
      IFVAR demhead ! 1
       ECHO PLAYER Loud laughter issues from the head, at the same time as a jet of flame covers you!
       ECHO OTHERS %N's efforts to push the %a are met by derisive laughter and a roaring jet of flame!
       DAMAGE BURN 200 Sheets of flame cover %N!
       EQUAL demhead1 0
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
