     ECHO PLAYER You hear a slight click as the head slides partway into the wall.
     ECHO OTHERS You hear a faint click as %N pushes the %a partway into the wall.
     EQUAL demhead1 3
     EQUAL demhead 1
    ENDIF
     IFVAR demhead1 ! 2
      IFVAR demhead ! 1
       ECHO PLAYER Loud laughter issues from the head, at the same time as twin bolts of lightning shoot from the eyes and hit you!
       ECHO OTHERS %N's efforts to push the %a are met by derisive laughter and twin bolts of lightning shooting from the eyes!
       DAMAGE ELECTRIC 200 Electricity crackles around %N!
       EQUAL demhead1 0
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH 4
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR demhead2 ! 1
   EQUAL demhead 0
    IFVAR demhead1 = 3
     ECHO PLAYER You hear a slight click as the head slides partway into the wall.
     ECHO OTHERS You hear a faint click as %N pushes the %a partway into the wall.
     ECHO ALL The central portion of the western wall slides up with a slow grating noise, leaving an opening through which bright light streams.
     NEWITEM 6 72 VAL2=1043
     EQUAL demhead1 4
     EQUAL demhead 1
     EQUAL demhead2 1
    ENDIF
     IFVAR demhead1 ! 3
      IFVAR demhead ! 1
       ECHO PLAYER Loud laughter issues from the head, at the same time as an evil black light flows from the eyes into you!
       ECHO OTHERS %N's efforts to push the %a are met by derisive laughter and an evil black light flowing from the eyes into %N!
       DAMAGE BODYONLY 200 Agony rips through %N's body!
       EQUAL demhead1 0
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
