NUMBER 3994
NAME Under Keep, shimmering wall
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The frozen hall ends to the north, at a shimmering wall of ice. Strange mists swirl within the icy surface of the wall, sending a slight shiver down your spine. Your breath hangs in the air, freezing solid with each exhale. The thick layers of ice covering the walls press in on you, nearly suffocating in their nearness, making you glance nervously at them. Above the wall are pulsating runes, that drip with blood and spell out, "Daraal".
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 3993
ITEM 0 420
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The mists clear and a number of images begin to rapidly flicker across your sight...an icy plain, filled with Darakoth... a looming castle of black ice... a storm of black snow that lands on the ground in flames... these, and other visions of horror, dance across your eyes. You feel insistent tugging on your mind... beckoning you, almost seductively...
*DESCRIPTION_END
