 IFVAR statblo = 5
  IFVAR INTNUM43 = 50
   ECHO PLAYER The statue leans close to you and whispers, "The Lord of the Black Hills, his true name is Ghir."
   ECHO OTHERS The statue leans close to %N.
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
