NUMBER 3999
NAME Under Keep, pillar
FIXED_LIGHT
DEEPCAVE
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Extending from the floor to the ceiling, flowing smoothly from one to the other, is a beautiful pillar of pure ice. The pillar glows with the captured light of thousands of tiny, polished gems that all seems to sparkle and turn within their icy prison. The illumination provided by the pillar keeps at bay the numerous shadows that flicker across the frigid walls of this passage.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT NW 1042
EXIT SE 3991
ITEM 0 420
ITEM 1 1700 ADJ1=165
EXTEND 1 with numerous sparkling gems captured inside it
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Pitch black stone stares back at you from behind the sheet of ice that is prevalent on the walls in this cold underground.
*DESCRIPTION_END
CALL 24
MONSTER_GROUP 81
VARIABLE thuwall
VARIABLE thuwall1
VARIABLE thuwall2
IFVERB CONCENTRATE 1
     ECHO PLAYER You let your mind flow towards the gems trapped within the ice pillar...you think you feel one of them, respond? It begins to slowly move towards you... just as its about to break free, you lose your link.
     ECHO OTHERS %N concetrates intently upon the pillar, oblivious to anything else.%c>%c%N curses loudly!
     EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
   ECHO PLAYER Very faintly you can hear a rhythmic thudding, it seems to vibrate through the walls around you.
   ECHO OTHERS %N leans close to the walls, listening intently.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH 0
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR thuwall1 = 1
   IFVAR thuwall = 3
    ECHO PLAYER The wall slides in and the rhythmic thudding seems to grow louder.
    ECHO OTHERS %N pushes on the wall, it seems to slide in slightly.
    EQUAL thuwall 4
    EQUAL thuwall1 2
    AFFECT 1042
    ECHO ALL The lid of the chest pops open!
    OPEN 3
    AFFECT 3999
   ENDIF
    IFVAR thuwall ! 3
     ECHO PLAYER The wall does not move as you push on it, and you hear a painful scream coming from the walls.
     ECHO OTHERS The wall resist %N's efforts to push on it, and you can faintly hear a painful scream coming from the walls.
     EQUAL thuwall 0
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
