ASTRAL
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This opulent room seems to have been used as a lounge of some kind. Plush chairs and couches sit, vacant, on a crimson rug. A polished oak table is the centerpiece of the room, a crystal chandelier hanging slightly above its reflective surface. The room seems like it has been unused for some time however, for cobwebs and dust cover all the items. The western wall has a couple of items of interest upon its face, and the southern wall contains an arch that leads into a side room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
